OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start on Wednesday
OL,6,Fmorning, particularly in the east with
OL,7,Fany mist or fog clearing. Turning
OL,8,Fincreasingly cloudy into the
OL,9,Fafternoon, though staying mostly dry.
OL,10,FSome rain arriving in the north by the
OL,11,Fevening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudier this evening with
OL,14,Frain pushing across the region.
OL,15,FTurning drier behind with clear spells
OL,16,Fand turning chilly with a touch of
OL,17,Frural frost. Breezy, but winds easing
OL,18,Fby dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
