OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA chillier start with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Sunshine turning hazy into the
OL,7,Fafternoon but remaining fine and dry
OL,8,Fwith light winds. Feeling cooler.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FTurning
OL,11,Funsettled over the Easter weekend with
OL,12,Fshowers or longer spells of rain.
OL,13,FGenerally drier and brighter on Easter
OL,14,FSunday. Some strong and gusty winds
OL,15,Ftoo.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
